commandText:
SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[CRM], [m].[Nome], [t].[Id], [t].[Descricao], [t].[EspecialidadesId], [t].[MedicosId]
FROM [Medicos] AS [m]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[Descricao], [e].[EspecialidadesId], [e].[MedicosId]
    FROM [EspecialidadeMedico] AS [e]
    INNER JOIN [Especialidades] AS [e0] ON [e].[EspecialidadesId] = [e0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[MedicosId]
ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[EspecialidadesId], [t].[MedicosId]
